data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: A little girl wearing a white sleeveless top and a pair of blue jeans is jogging on the road. She has blonde hair and fair skin. And she is quite skinny. Her arms are swinging as she leaps off the ground. She is looking to her right. I suppose there is probably something interesting attracting her attention. In the background, there are a couple of bushes and massive rocks. It looks like it is in summer. (76字)
